                           <desc>: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#103v">103v</locus>: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ቀርን፡ ሰበር፡
